OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FLargely dry
OL,6,Fin the east throughout Monday evening
OL,7,Fwith late sunny spells. Scattered
OL,8,Fshowers affecting western coasts
OL,9,Finitially, then tending to spread a
OL,10,Flittle further inland overnight and
OL,11,Fturn locally heavy around dawn. A cool
OL,12,Fnight for June.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTuesday:FA day of sunshine and
OL,15,Fblustery showers, though the showers
OL,16,Ftending to become more isolated and
OL,17,Flighter during the afternoon. Pleasant
OL,18,Fin the sun but temperatures a little
OL,19,Fbelow average.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
